console.log("CEP digitado:", cep); try { const resposta = await fetch(`${API_URL}/api/cep/${cep}`); const data = await resposta.json(); if (!resposta.ok || data.erro) { setErroCep("CEP não encontrado"); if(cpf.length !== 11){ return } if (cpf.length !== 11 || /^(\d)\1{10}$/.test(cpf)) return false; // Verifica CPF inválido let sum = 0; for (let i = 0; i < 9; i++) sum += parseInt(cpf[i]) * (10 - i); let firstVerifier = 11 - (sum % 11); if (firstVerifier === 10 || firstVerifier === 11) firstVerifier = 0; sum = 0; for (let i = 0; i < 10; i++) sum += parseInt(cpf[i]) * (11 - i); let secondVerifier = 11 - (sum % 11); if (secondVerifier === 10 || secondVerifier === 11) secondVerifier = 0; return cpf[9] === firstVerifier.toString() && cpf[10] === secondVerifier.toString(); }; return( <>
